name: Pack of 3 Limited Edition Postcards
description:
Shell Graham: Limited Edition of 50 Signed and Numbered postcard prints

Pack of three postcards: Numbers in pack may vary as designs have also be sold individually.

Postcard is part of a series of work created to advertise a ficticious breakfast treat: Pop'd Arts. More info about me, my work and all that jazz can be found at: www.commershell.com

Postcard print will be packed and delivered in order of purchase, therefore the sooner you get you mits on one of these lovelies the sooner on in the edition process your print will be!
Thanks for looking and happy shopping!!!

name: Campbell's Soup Tin Slippers 6 -7
description:
'One Off' art work! Slippers were hand-made by myself and appeared in the video 'Artvertisement 03' that won the 'PKF Top Design Award 2008'.
As they are video props they are a little worn on the bottom due to all that dancing, but this just adds to the history and purpose of them!
I plan in the future to try and get these babies mass produced, however the machine will not be able to capture the arty, handcrafted loveliness of this version.
Slippers come with a signed certificate of authenticity! These slippers fit a size 6-7, however they are to be appreciated more as artwork than foot ware...
